        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ Master's (30) + 4 years (10) + Under 30 (20) + English B1 (10) = 70 points. Qualified for shortage occupation route (IT). Got card in 10 weeks. ÖGK automatic, using Docfinder app to find English-speaking doctors.</p>
