        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ PhD gives maximum qualification points. German B1 (15) + age (15) = well over 70. Classified as "very highly qualified"—no labor market test needed. Fast processing, card in 6 weeks. Added UNIQA supplement for private hospital access.</p>
