        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ Bachelor's (20) + 6+ years (20) + age 30-40 (15) + English B1 (10) = 65 points. Borderline! Took German A2 course during application = 10 more points = 75. Got card after 12 weeks. Learning German was worth it for points and daily life.</p>
