        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">✗ Bachelor's (20) + 2 years experience (no points, need 3+) + age under 25 (0, not in points) + English (10) = only 30 points. Far below threshold. Would need Master's degree or 6+ years experience to qualify. Advised to study in Austria first or gain experience.</p>
